                  "body": {
                    "type": "TextualBody",
                    "value": "<p rend=\"align(right)\"><placeName>New York</placeName>, <date>Feby 12/66</date>.</p>\n            <p><addressee>Rev. I Leeser</addressee>,</p>\n            <p rend=\"indent(1)\">Dear Sir and Friend,</p>\n            <p>I wished to see you when I was<lb/> at home on <date>Sunday</date> last, but had<lb/>\n                not the opportunity to do so.<lb/> As my preceptor and very old friend, I<lb/> deem\n                it my duty and at the same<lb/> time a pleasure to inform you of<lb/> my engagement\n                to <persName>miss Julia Spanier</persName><lb/> formerly of\n                    <placeName>Albany</placeName>, but now of this<lb/> city — I think you are\n                well<lb/> acquainted with the family, and I trust<lb/> to have the pleasure ere long\n                of introducing<lb/> you to the young lady I drop you<lb/> these few lines, as I know\n                they they will<lb/> give you pleasure, and am as always,</p>\n            <p rend=\"indent(10)\">Your very true friend,</p>\n            <p rend=\"indent(10)\"><persName role=\"author\">M. M. Allen</persName>,</p>\n            <p>(Over)</p>"
                  },
                  "target": "https://colenda.library.upenn.edu/items/ark:/81431/p3qb9vn83/canvas/p1"
                }
              ]
            }
