                    "type": "TextualBody",
                    "value": "<p>P. S. I received this last week<lb/>\n                <hi rend=\"underline\">credentials</hi> for the orthodox <add>אמונת אבותינו</add><lb/>\n                <add>קהלה</add> of <placeName>Fort Wayne</placeName>, to represent<lb/> them in the\n                “Board of American Israelites”<lb/>\n                <persName role=\"author\">M.</persName></p>\n        </body>\n    </text>\n</TEI>"
